**Privacy Policy**

Last updated: March 16, 2026

Craftory respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use the Craftory mobile application.

## 1. Information We Collect

### Account Information

When you create an account, we may collect:

* Email address
* User ID
* Authentication information

### Business Data

When using Craftory, you may provide:

* Product information
* Inventory data
* Material records
* Orders
* Uploaded images

### Usage Data

We may collect limited technical information such as:

* Device type
* App version
* Basic usage analytics

## 2. How We Use Information

We use collected information to:

* Provide and maintain the Service
* Store and sync your business data
* Improve app functionality
* Provide support when requested
* Ensure the security of the platform

We do not sell your personal data.

## 3. Cloud Storage

Craftory stores user data using cloud services such as Firebase. These providers may process data on our behalf under their own security and privacy policies.

## 4. Data Security

We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data. However, no internet transmission or storage system can be guaranteed to be completely secure.

## 5. Data Retention

We retain your data only for as long as your account is active or as necessary to provide the Service.

If you delete your account, we will delete or anonymize your data within a reasonable timeframe.

## 6. Your Rights

Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:

* Access your data
* Correct inaccurate information
* Request deletion of your data

You can contact us to request these actions.

## 7. Children's Privacy

Craftory is not intended for individuals under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal data from children.

## 8. Changes to this Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted within the app or on our website.

## 9. Contact

If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

